| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4651 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonransomware)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 00632ec2-6156-53fe-896b-5c5a3afc92c5"
